        "most_recent": [
          {
            "id": "ec9c8256-950b-4756-9c38-6c9c63242c68",
            "text": "I love it, small but brightens the room well.",
            "author": {
              "nickname": "natasha",
              "external_id": "7920365306"
            },
            "title": "Little light of mine",
            "rating": {
              "value": 5.0,
              "submitted_at": "2026-03-31T16:26:37.290Z"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "eb05a2a0-cab9-44bb-a366-44b63496ae81",
            "text": "Don\u2019t bother with this junk. You can\u2019t replace the bulb when it goes out, so it needs to be trashed!!!! So basically, it\u2019s a disposable lamp. So wasteful!",
            "author": {
              "nickname": "mvillarreal",
              "external_id": "7996465884"
            },
            "title": "Landfillcore",
            "rating": {
              "value": 1.0,
              "submitted_at": "2026-02-19T01:08:12.214Z"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "46bd09ac-c770-48d1-8e34-220d68e729c5",
            "text": "This light worked well for about 2 years before it started very aggresivly flickering when you turn it on. it also turned on once in the middle of the light while it was fully off. And they dont have any way for you to access the light bulb or fix it.",
            "author": {
              "nickname": "Not really worth it",
              "external_id": "7975777104"
            },
            "title": "Does Not Last",
            "rating": {
              "value": 2.0,
              "submitted_at": "2026-02-02T01:34:41.961Z"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "c18396e1-c2f5-4b16-8728-bf331d2be078",
            "text": "USB charger doesn't work",
            "author": {
              "nickname": "Wendy",
              "external_id": "10014495311"
            },
            "rating": {
              "value": 1.0,
              "submitted_at": "2026-01-24T19:54:49.025Z"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "a29e09e0-ea17-4afa-8064-1cedd1be9a4b",
            "text": "I thought this was cordless. Wrong! Be aware that it isn't. Still, it looked nice in my space and while I didn't think it's worth 40 bucks I kept it. Then I knocked it over. It shattered easily. 40 bucks for a week of lighting. Oh well.",
            "author": {
              "nickname": "Jr",
              "external_id": "7977773332"
            },
            "rating": {
              "value": 2.0,
              "submitted_at": "2025-11-21T23:33:41.568Z"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "c14fa2ce-08bb-4454-8d6c-4e8eb5910dc5",
            "text": "Good function and pretty small size lamp. I wish the color of the light was more on the warm side. Going to try it out as part of newborn\u2019s middle of the night chang up set up. However, majority suggests using red light or warm light so I am hesitant to say this is a good option for this set up.",
            "author": {
              "nickname": "Jackie",
              "external_id": "20002296745"
            },
            "title": "Good lamp but wish it's warmer light",
            "rating": {
              "value": 4.0,
              "submitted_at": "2025-11-09T17:37:53.970Z"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "39fee327-8192-44ae-ae11-d13e5046964f",
            "text": "cute little lamp. love the brightness for the size and the dimming function",
            "author": {
              "nickname": "tabetha",
              "external_id": "20066393319"
            },
            "rating": {
