          "downstream_description": "Illuminate your favorite reading nook with this USB Ports Desk Lamp from Threshold\u2122. Boasting an oval glass shade with a wooden base, this lamp adds a touch of natural appeal to your home decor while illuminating your space with just the right amount of light. The non-removable integrated LED bulb creates a soft glow, while the full-range dimmable setting allows you to create the perfect ambiance. Place it on the side table next to your sofa or on a console table in your living room for an inviting look, and use the two USB ports to charge your devices.<br /><br />Threshold\u2122: Looks like home, feels like you.",
